# Pocket Lawyer

## User stories 

### Home page
  - As a user I can send a emergency request.
  - As a user I can sign-in.
  - As a user I can see my conversations.
  - As a user I can explore the database. 

### Conversation page
  - As a user I can open conversations.

### Message page
  - As a user I can rate resolutions.
  - As a user I can confirm resolutions.
  - As a user I share results.

### Result Page
  - As a user I can see reviews.
  - AS a user I can open questions and answers.
  - As a user I can contact lawyer. 

## Nouns
- users
- conversations
- questions( answers as a column)
- laywers

